The paper discusses the challenges of query processing in the presence of inferences in RDF database systems, which falls under the category of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also proposes a structured resource identification scheme using encoding of concepts and property hierarchies, which involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and deep learning (cs.DL) techniques. The paper also mentions the use of Apache Spark framework for implementation, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and software engineering (cs.SE).
